Create KPI Cards Stages 3-6 12

Visual 3

1. Select the card visual

2. Add Accident/Month Measure  into the fields

3. In the format column go to the general Tab  and input the following specifics X Position 460, Width 208, height 98

4. On the Data Label Tab:  Font Color Black, Text Size 27, Font DIN

5. Turn Of Category Label

6. On the Title Tab; Rename title to Accident/Month, Background Color#094780, text size 11 , Font DIN

7. On the Border Tab: Choose  Color Black
